{"type": "article", "id": 28601, "title": "调料瓶组合", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-23T06:51:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021616209VAzmOZEy7xlkhsD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>优秀的仿生设计不仅有能让人会心一笑的造型，也不失实用性。今天介绍的这款调味瓶组合 AJORÍ 就是西班牙的设计团队 photoAlquimia 从大蒜瓣中获取的灵感。它由中央的球茎（木质提杆）和六片蒜瓣（陶瓷调料瓶）组成，优雅独特的外形不仅耐看也很适合厨房的环境。这是它的购买<a href=\"http://www.shop.photoalquimia.com/collections/natura-imitatis/products/ajori\">链接</a>，售价为 260 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161617WtvKCk7NTmErflcs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71181102\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021616188GoxXjkTqlDbnpfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66631579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161618c6ZJxGlAkRiMBXjK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161619Ad8HR9Q2OlhxXBsJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75052632\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}